 dwarf, halfling, barbarian, erudite, gnome, and all of the elves.  We do this because it is very hard to distinguish between the sexes of a Troll, Ogre, or Iksar (especially the Iksar : )<br><br>Man will be introduced first, and will have many unique powers and abilities.  In addition to the daily allowance of food and water, man will also be required to carry along some type of alcohol with him at all times. (Don’t worry if you think you can’t afford the high price of beer we will also be adding a new type of alcohol called Malt Liquor which will be very cheap).  <br>Man will also be given new skills called: Lie, Cheat, Compartmentalize, and Ignore the emotions of others.  Lie is a new skill which allows all Men to distract one mob while he pummels away at another.  This used in combination with cheat is very powerful and allows Man to maintain several battles with mobs at once (this can pose a problem because if any of the mobs find out the Man is cheating on them…the will enrage and cast a 32000 pt. DD spell on man instantly slaying him). <br> Man will have another skill that is similar to bind wound called Scratch Nuts.  This causes slight healing but if done too much Man will develop Rash, which is a minor poison-based DOT spell.<br>Man has naturally high STR and naturally low INT.  Man however is very high in the new stat called Common Sense (abbrev. CMS).<br>Stats and abilities will not vary between races because men are all basically the same all around the world ; )<br><br>The other new class Woman is complete with a huge list of special abilities including…Nag, Intuition, Bitch-slap, and the ultimate….PMS.  Woman is also required to visit a vendor at least once every Everquest Week.  This is the so-called Shopping Penalty Verant has decided to use to balance the classes.  <br>Nag is a new skill is a combination of taunt and fear.  The mob is angered at the woman, but if it is nagged too much it will run away.<br>Intuition is much like track except that it is always right, and has the ability to sense the presence of men who will ruin their girlfriend’s lives.<br>Bitch-slap is a variation of bash but can only be used on female opponents and in duels with male players that have insulted the Woman.<br>Woman’s most powerful attribute is PMS.  A Woman will only go into PMS mode once every Everquest month, but during this time she acts the same way a warrior does in berserker mode, or an NPC on enrage.  A Woman in PMS is nearly unstoppable when facing enemies, an unfortunate side effect of this is that sometime a PMS woman may attack her party members and slay them…but don’t worry its only hormones ; )<br>Women have high AGI, and CHA, and have a large amount of the new stat Emotion (abbrev. EMO).<br><br>We hope that these new classes will add fun to you EQ experience.<br>Verant<br><br>Josiah Supertank<br>48th Warrior<br>Forsaken Dreams<br><br>~Damn it feels good to be a Gangstah~<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ustagnok.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Stagnok</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 13<br> <font color=#E9D756>(11/7/01 11:56:53 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm17.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=221.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Funny Idea for new Classes </span><hr size=1> That is pretty good <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p>Stagnok28 WarriorSheahay16 Druid</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#575757><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/umalevant.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Malevant</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 13<br> <font color=#E9D75